# Vision Container Scripts

`record_scan.py` depends on `pyorbbecsdk` and `cv2`, which are installed in the **vision_comp** container (Ubuntu 22.04 + Python 3.10).

Run with:

```bash
docker compose exec vision_comp record-scan --object <name> --description "<desc>"
```

For local development without Docker, use the host vision env:

```bash
/home/lq/miniconda3/envs/vision/bin/python docker_all/components/vision_comp/app/vision_server/scripts/record_scan.py [args...]
```

Never use `tbp.monty` env or bare `python` — they lack the camera SDK.
